001,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/06\/hijamah-cupping-incense\/","url_meta":{"origin":18999,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Hijamah: Best of your treatments are cupping, sea incense","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the best practice with which you treat yourselves is cupping and sea incense. Do not torture your children with sore throats by pressing their throats with your fingers, but rather you must use incense.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8161,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/blackseed-cure-except-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":18999,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Healing properties of blackseed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"This blackseed is healing for all diseases but poison.\u201d She said, \u201cWhat is poison?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cDeath.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5363 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0627\u0626\u0634\u0629 \u0642\u0627\u0644\u062a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32714,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/cures-physical-mental-spiritual\/","url_meta":{"origin":18999,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Healing: Cures for every physical, mental, spiritual disease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah did not send down any disease but that he also sent down the cure.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5354 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Ibn al-Qayyim said, \u201cThis is generally true for diseases of the heart, the spirit, the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":771,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/10\/no-healing-but-you\/","url_meta":{"origin":18999,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Healing: Take away the pain by Your healing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 10, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would visit a sick person, he would say,\u00a0\u201cTake away the pain, O Lord of all people, and give healing for You are the Healer. There is no healing but Your healing, a healing that leaves no trace\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/22\/treat-with-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":18999,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ruqyah: Treat your sick ones with the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 22, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, entered upon her as a woman was treating her illness or performing recitations over her. The Prophet said, \u201cTreat her with the book of Allah.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 6098 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41237,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/27\/allah-removes-pain\/","url_meta":{"origin":18999,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ruqyah: Calling upon Allah alone to remove pain","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 27, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abd al-Aziz reported: Thabit and I entered the home of Anas ibn Malik, and Thabit said, \u201cO Abu Hamzah, I am complaining of pain.\u201d Anas said, \u201cShall I not invoke over you with the incantation of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him?\u201d Thabit said, \u201cOf course.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":